    "/api/questions/{id}/submit": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Question"],
        "summary": "문제 제출",
        "description": "## 인증(JWT): **불필요**\n\n## 요청 헤더\n- **`X-User-UUID`**: 회원 UUID\n\n## 요청 파라미터\n- **`id`**: 문제 ID (path variable)\n\n## 요청 바디\n- **`selectedKey`**: 선택한 선택지 키 (String)\n\n## 반환값 (SubmitResult)\n- 정답 여부, 정답 선택지, AI 해설 여부 등\n\n\n**API 변경 이력:**\n\u003Ctable\u003E\u003Cthead\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Cth\u003E날짜\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E작성자\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E이슈번호\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E이슈 제목\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E변경 내용\u003C/th\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/thead\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E2026.04.07\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E서새찬\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://github.com/passQL-Lab/passQL/issues/1\" target=\"_blank\"\u003E#1\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003EAI 서버 및 Spring 서버 초기 프로젝트 구성\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E문제 제출 API 추가\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/tbody\u003E\u003C/table\u003E",
        "operationId": "submit",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "format": "int64"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "X-User-UUID",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "additionalProperties": {
                  "type": "string"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SubmitResult"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/questions/{id}/execute": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Question"],
        "summary": "SQL 실행 (테스트)",
        "description": "## 인증(JWT): **불필요**\n\n## 요청 파라미터\n- **`id`**: 문제 ID (path variable)\n\n## 요청 바디\n- **`sql`**: 실행할 SQL (String)\n\n## 반환값 (ExecuteResult)\n- SQL 실행 결과 (컬럼, 행 데이터)\n- 제출이 아닌 테스트 실행이므로 채점하지 않음\n\n\n**API 변경 이력:**\n\u003Ctable\u003E\u003Cthead\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Cth\u003E날짜\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E작성자\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E이슈번호\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E이슈 제목\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E변경 내용\u003C/th\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/thead\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E2026.04.07\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E서새찬\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://github.com/passQL-Lab/passQL/issues/1\" target=\"_blank\"\u003E#1\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003EAI 서버 및 Spring 서버 초기 프로젝트 구성\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003ESQL 실행(테스트) API 추가\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/tbody\u003E\u003C/table\u003E",
        "operationId": "executeChoice",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "format": "int64"
            }
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "additionalProperties": {
                  "type": "string"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ExecuteResult"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/members/register": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Member"],
        "summary": "익명 회원 등록",
        "description": "## 인증(JWT): **불필요**\n\n## 요청 파라미터\n- 없음\n\n## 반환값 (MemberRegisterResponse)\n- **`memberUuid`**: 발급된 회원 UUID\n- **`nickname`**: 자동 생성된 닉네임\n\n## 설명\n- UUID와 닉네임을 자동 발급한다.\n- 닉네임은 서버에서 랜덤 생성된다.\n\n\n**API 변경 이력:**\n\u003Ctable\u003E\u003Cthead\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Cth\u003E날짜\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E작성자\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E이슈번호\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E이슈 제목\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E변경 내용\u003C/th\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/thead\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E2026.04.07\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E서새찬\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://github.com/passQL-Lab/passQL/issues/6\" target=\"_blank\"\u003E#6\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003EMember 도메인 모듈 신규 생성 및 확장성 있는 Entity 설계 필요\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E익명 회원 등록 API 추가\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/tbody\u003E\u003C/table\u003E",
        "operationId": "register",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/MemberRegisterResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/members/me/regenerate-nickname": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Member"],
        "summary": "닉네임 재생성",
        "description": "## 인증(JWT): **불필요**\n\n## 요청 파라미터\n- **`memberUuid`**: 회원 UUID (query param)\n\n## 반환값 (NicknameRegenerateResponse)\n- **`nickname`**: 새로 발급된 닉네임\n\n## 설명\n- 본인 닉네임을 새로 발급한다.\n\n\n**API 변경 이력:**\n\u003Ctable\u003E\u003Cthead\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Cth\u003E날짜\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E작성자\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E이슈번호\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E이슈 제목\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E변경 내용\u003C/th\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/thead\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E2026.04.07\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E서새찬\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://github.com/passQL-Lab/passQL/issues/6\" target=\"_blank\"\u003E#6\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003EMember 도메인 모듈 신규 생성 및 확장성 있는 Entity 설계 필요\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E닉네임 재생성 API 추가\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/tbody\u003E\u003C/table\u003E",
        "operationId": "regenerateNickname",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "memberUuid",
            "in": "query",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "uuid"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/NicknameRegenerateResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/ai/explain-error": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["AI"],
        "summary": "SQL 에러 해설",
        "description": "## 인증(JWT): **불필요**\n\n## 요청 헤더\n- **`X-User-UUID`**: 회원 UUID\n\n## 요청 바디\n- **`questionId`**: 문제 ID (Long)\n- **`sql`**: 실행한 SQL (String)\n- **`errorMessage`**: 발생한 에러 메시지 (String)\n\n## 반환값 (AiResult)\n- AI가 생성한 에러 해설\n\n\n**API 변경 이력:**\n\u003Ctable\u003E\u003Cthead\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Cth\u003E날짜\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E작성자\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E이슈번호\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E이슈 제목\u003C/th\u003E\u003Cth\u003E변경 내용\u003C/th\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/thead\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E2026.04.07\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E서새찬\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://github.com/passQL-Lab/passQL/issues/1\" target=\"_blank\"\u003E#1\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003EAI 서버 및 Spring 서버 초기 프로젝트 구성\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003ESQL 에러 AI 해설 API 추가\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/tbody\u003E\u003C/table\u003E",
        "operationId": "explainError",
        "parameters": [
